title: EU-Turkey joint action plan (European Commission - Directorate-General for Enlargement)
text: ( Source : European Commission - Directorate-General for Enlargement ) Challenges are common and responses need to be coordinated. Negotiating candidate country Turkey and the EU are determined to confront and surmount the existing challenges
